{"results":[{"aya":"036","id":3824,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"并且说：难道我们务必要为一个狂妄的诗人，而抛弃我们的众神灵吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"037","id":3825,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"不然！他昭示了真理，并证实了历代的使者。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"038","id":3826,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"你们必定尝试痛苦的刑罚，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"039","id":3827,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"你们只依自己的行为而受报酬。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"040","id":3828,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"惟真主的虔诚的众仆，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"041","id":3829,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"将享受一种可知的给养--","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"042","id":3830,"locale":"zh","sura":"037","text":"各种水果，同时他们是受优待的；","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":26,"previousPage":"/zh/s037-5.json","nextPage":"/zh/s037-7.json"}}